name: Weeping Jug
description: I crouched painfully and reached my jug. The jug I spelled to be a light whenever the shadow consumes my strength. The lid was broken, it left me with emptiness. Now I realized that that is all I have. I keep hugging my jug thight and cover the openings so that this emptiness wont go as well. It’s slowly turning into a weeping jug now.
